34:35.441 --> 34:37.143
It is very complicated.

34:39.211 --> 34:42.214
But I do know...

34:45.851 --> 34:48.053
...I want you to be happy,
Lea.

34:48.187 --> 34:52.124
****

34:52.258 --> 34:55.527
I have so many reasons
to do this.

34:59.331 --> 35:00.766
And so many doubts.

35:02.868 --> 35:04.970
I'm just scared, Shaun.

35:07.839 --> 35:11.743
